        "TileImage": "$($repository 5403294c-5390-46ba-a246-4bb6108253c0).Image",
        "Description": "Have you ever looked at a Hitman NPC and thought: &quot;Man, how I would massacre you if only you weren&apos;t a non target...&quot;? Well then you&apos;ve come to the right place pal! In this contract series I will pick out the most infuriating NPCs in each mission so that you can kill them without regret :)\r\rDante Woods is my single most hated NPC in the entire Hitman Trilogy.\rIf you&apos;ve ever thrown a coin in the library, you know why",
